definition: classifier indicating a small amount or small number greater than 1: some, a few, several

sentences.english: Earlier this week Kuttner announced he was stepping down from his role
sentences.chinese: 本週早些時候，庫特納宣佈將辭去自己的職務。

sentences.english: The luxury naturist holiday spot opened its doors earlier this year.
sentences.chinese: 這家豪華的礦泉療養旅館在今年早些時候已經開業。

sentences.english: If you want your baby born early, you can eat scrambled eggs castor oil .
sentences.chinese: 如果想讓寶寶早些出生，你可以喫些蓖麻油炒雞蛋。

sentences.english: He recalled what he read in the book earlier.
sentences.chinese: 他回憶起今天早些時候他在書上看到的。

sentences.english: I would have introduced Wright-Phillips and Robben a lot earlier.
sentences.chinese: 要是我，就早些換上羅本和小賴特。

sentences.english: The Reserve Bank of Australia kept rates on hold early this morning as the market expected.
sentences.chinese: 澳洲聯儲今天早些時候維持利率，且在市場意料中。

sentences.english: Reports on India and Brazil were released earlier in the year.
sentences.chinese: 印度和巴西的報告已經在今年早些時候公佈。

sentences.english: Word of this follows earlier proposals from political advisors, calling on the government to relax the policy.
sentences.chinese: 這來自政協委員們的早些建議，呼籲政府放寬政策。

sentences.english: The earlier buyers want their money back.
sentences.chinese: 這些早些的購主，向開放商要回他們的錢。

sentences.english: North Korea threatened to shoot at the speakers earlier this year.
sentences.chinese: 北朝鮮今年早些時候威脅要射殺這些喊話者。

sentences.english: I shall intreat his pardon for not having done it earlier.
sentences.chinese: 我一定去求他原諒，請他不要怪我沒有早些問候他。

sentences.english: Jacobs would like to set up an interview for early next week.
sentences.chinese: 雅可布先生想在下週早些時候約你面談一次。

sentences.english: In one sense the situation is more critical than in earlier years.
sentences.chinese: 從這個意義上說，現在的情況比早些年更嚴重。

sentences.english: Thousands of Timorese protested outside the Australian embassy earlier this year.
sentences.chinese: 今年早些時候許多東帝汶人在澳大利亞大使館外抗議。

sentences.english: Moscow suspended its visa free policy with Turkey earlier this week.
sentences.chinese: 俄方也在這周早些時候暫停了土耳其的免籤政策。

sentences.english: Earlier that day, inthe hospital, she had reprimanded him about a mistake he'd made, and now he wasdesperate to find out how he could redeem himself.
sentences.chinese: 當天早些時候，他由於犯錯，被她嚴厲地斥責了一番。
